Data Binding:

-share data inside th component

Types of Data Binding:
1. One way Biding(one direction data flow):
    -ts file- component
    -html file - view

    1.1. Component to view(changes happening from ts->html)
        a). String interpolation - {{expression}}
        b). Property binding - [attribute_name] = "property"

    1.2. View to component(changes happens from html->ts)
        a). Event binding -(event_name) = "function_name()"
        b).Even binfing- $event-(event_name)="function_name($event)"
        c)Event binding using template referencing variable - #variable_name

2. Two way binding:
        [(ngmodel)]="property"


Angular Routing: to set a path for a component

    {
        path:value,component:class_name
    }

    Angular services
    
    Angular Directives: To manipulate DOM elements
        a) Component Directives
        b) Structural Directives
            1)ngFor



    Angular Forms:
        a)Template driven Forms
        b)Model driven Forms
            1)Reactive formsModule
            